Titolo: Field of Fire (video game)

Anno: 1984

Descrizione: Field of Fire is a computer wargame for the Atari 8-bit family designed by Roger Damon and published by the Strategic Simulations in 1984. The game was ported to the Commodore 64 by Brian Fitzgerald. A version for the Apple II was also released. Roger Damon also wrote Operation Whirlwind.